name: Nike
description: Inspired by the original that debuted in 1985, the Air Jordan 1 Low delivers a clean, classic look that's familiar yet fresh. With an iconic design that blends seamlessly with any fit, these shoes are perfect for taking charge. Advantages: - Encapsulated Air-Sole unit for lightweight cushioning. - Genuine leather on the upper for durability and a premium look. - Solid rubber outsole for greater traction on different types of surfaces. - Color Shown: Palomino/White/Wild Berry - Model: 553558-215 - Proven efficacy A timeless rubber sole combines with a soft sockliner and encapsulated Nike Air cushioning for all-day comfort. The rubber outsole offers durable traction on a variety of surfaces.
